name: KitchenHelper
0: ”Alexa, open Kitchen Helper and recommend a recipe.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: kitchen helper
des: Kitchen Helper solves the dilemma of what's for dinner by providing meal suggestions. Simply give it a main ingredient and a course (breakfast, lunch or dinner) and it will return 5 meal ideas. Future implementations will return the full recipe.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
